amores-Hayley-Williams-and-Talking-Heads-David-Byrne.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paramores-Hayley-Williams-and-Talking-Heads-David-Byrne-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paramores-Hayley-Williams-and-Talking-Heads-David-Byrne-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paramores-Hayley-Williams-and-Talking-Heads-David-Byrne-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paramores-Hayley-Williams-and-Talking-Heads-David-Byrne-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paramores-Hayley-Williams-and-Talking-Heads-David-Byrne-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/paramore">帕拉莫尔 (Paramore)</a>在清除社交媒体后宣布回归，并以翻唱作为<a href="/artists/talking-heads">Talking Heads</a>致敬专辑的一部分。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/paramore-cover-interview-2023-this-is-why-3396051"><b>封面上的帕拉莫尔：“我希望没有年轻女性经历我所做的事情”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月，由 Hayley Williams、吉他手 Taylor York 和鼓手 Zac Farro 组成的三人组删除了社交媒体页面上的所有帖子和图片，同时他们的<a href="https://www.paramore.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方网站</a>显示了 404 错误消息。在此之前，乐队在完成“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/paramore-this-is-why-album-review-3393080">This Is Why</a> ”巡演并最近履行了对唱片公司的义务后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-on-the-future-of-the-band-theres-a-level-of-uncertainty-3559192">对他们的未来表示了“一定程度的不确定性”</a> 。</p><p>关于该乐队的更多猜测于上周出现，当时有消息称他们将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-drop-out-out-alter-ego-fest-headline-performance-after-fan-speculation-and-wiping-social-accounts-3565973">退出 ALTer Ego 音乐节的头条表演，</a>随后有报道称 Paramore <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-reportedly-gearing-up-for-new-era-and-new-record-deal-3567133">正在为新时代和新唱片合约做好准备</a>。</p><p>现在，三人又开始活动了。今天（1 月 10 日）回到 Instagram，Paramore 分享了他们翻唱 Talking Heads 即将发行的致敬专辑《Burning Down The House》的预告片。</p><p>这段视频显示，女主唱海莉·<a href="/artists/hayley-williams">威廉姆斯 (Hayley Williams)</a>正在领取一个送到她家的包裹。打开后，她发现了 Talking Heads 主唱<a href="/artists/DAVID-BYRNE">David Byrne</a>标志性的超大西装，他在乐队的演唱会电影《Stop Making Sense》中就穿着这套西装。</p><p>然后，威廉姆斯从音箱顶部拉出一盘磁带，转向她的乐队成员说：“我有一盘磁带，我想为你们演奏，”伯恩在介绍歌曲“Burning Down The”时也说过同样的话。演唱会电影中的House。 Paramore 翻唱的歌曲作为预告片中的背景音频。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C17E1xyrMQ9/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.6